title: Notice of Public MeetingThe Harbor Sanitary District Board
text:
Notice of Public MeetingThe Harbor Sanitary District Board ad date: 10/07/2015 
Notice of Public MeetingThe Harbor Sanitary District Board of Directors will hold a Regular Meeting October 13, 2015 at 7:00 p.m. at the Harbor Sanitary District Building, 16408 Lower Harbor Rd., Brookings, OR.Subjects to be considered: 1. SDC Extension East Hoffeldt 2. Resolution 15-07-R A Resolution adopting Credit Card Policies 3. Resolution 15-08-R A Resolution transferring funds 4. Resolution 15-09-R A Resolution adopting revised Personnel PoliciesRalph Martin, Board ChairmanPublish October 7, 2015No. 71111425
